"You may see your mother as many times as you wish. Tranquility, I 
believe her name was. I picked up alot when I touched your spark."

Vulois noticed some bot yelling at him over a few feet. He went to 
him.

"What? Oh, you're that bot from the gateway. My name is Vulois, and 
this is my peace embassy. We were investigating it. To understand why 
would take many a day of story-telling. Let me give you the basic: I 
am on a peace mission to take everyone back to Cybertron, and this 
portal might be the way to get us there. Now, I have told you my name 
and why I was at the gateway, maybe you can tell me your name and why 
you were there, if you don't mind."
